attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Affordable modern NYC loft style Junior 1 Bed condominium with 1 off-street parking space located in the desirable Fort Point Channel area of the Seaport.  The high ceilings, large windows, exposed brick walls, timber columns and ceiling beams give the wide open space a flexible floor plan with distinct character and lots of architectural detail!  The hardwood floors, high end stainless steel kitchen appliances, deep farmers sink and sea glass/stone countertops are the perfect complement to this trendy urban loft style unit.  Tall custom designed wardrobes provide ample storage capacity and creates a sleeping area of distinction and privacy within this airy interior space.  The multipurpose luxurious bathroom has a deep tub, shower, large washer and dryer and a complementary wall of storage cabinets, shelves and drawers that will help keep this room neat and organize. Lastly, enjoy the comfort of central a/c and the convenience of an elevator building!  Pet friendly too!!
